text: Jananaayakan is a 1999 Indian Malayalam film, directed by Nissar, starring Babu Antony and Mumtaj in the lead role. ==Cast== * Babu Antony as Rajmohan * Mumtaj as Nancy perera * Lal as Misra * Jagathy Sreekumar as Ayyappan * Indrans as Thottapalli Thomman * Harisree Ashokan as Domenic * Devan as Sathyapalan * Saikumar as C.I Eliyas * Rajan P Dev as ambisami * Ajay Ratnam as Kuppuswami *Antony Thekkek- Cameo Appearance *Kaviyoor Renuka - Cameo Appearance *Mansoor Ali Khan - Cameo Appearance ==References== ==External links== * Category:1990 films Category:Indian films Category:1990s Malayalam- language films
